243
00:12:58,824 --> 00:13:00,134
S'il vous plaît ?

244
00:13:03,334 --> 00:13:06,034
Alors, plus de missions pour ce soir ok ?

245
00:13:06,414 --> 00:13:08,814
Oui, Fluttershy !
- On le promet, Fluttershy!

246
00:13:09,024 --> 00:13:10,104
- Bonne nuit, Fluttershy!

247
00:13:10,604 --> 00:13:12,214
Okay, bonne nuit.

248
00:13:15,914 --> 00:13:18,084
