Allons les filles, on ne va pas trouver ce poulet
ou nos cutie marks en se disputant.

293
00:15:43,768 --> 00:15:46,508
Peut-être que c'est notre talent caché. La dispute.

294
00:15:46,788 --> 00:15:47,588
Non !

295
00:15:47,588 --> 00:15:48,578
Si !

296
00:15:48,578 --> 00:15:50,428
- Non !
- Si !

297
00:15:50,428 --> 00:15:51,648
Il y a quelque chose ?

298
00:15:51,868 --> 00:15:52,808
Nope.

299
00:15:53,438 --> 00:15:54,028
- Mince.

300
00:15:57,168 --> 00:15:58,658
Iciiiii, pou-pou-pou-poulet !

301
00:16:02,588 --> 00:16:05,138
les filles ?
les filles ?

302
00:16:08,178 --> 00:16:09,828
