377
00:20:30,528 --> 00:20:31,678
Toi et Rarity.

378
00:20:32,468 --> 00:20:33,348
Bonjour, Rarity.

379
00:20:33,908 --> 00:20:35,608
As-tu terminé toutes ces capes ?

380
00:20:35,938 --> 00:20:37,448
