00:20:56,868 --> 00:20:57,538
Vos affaires !

392
00:20:58,318 --> 00:20:58,908
Les filles !

393
00:21:00,138 --> 00:21:00,938
Il est temps de--

394
00:21:02,298 --> 00:21:03,098
LES FILLES !

395
00:21:03,688 --> 00:21:04,248
Si tu me le permets...

396
00:21:05,738 --> 00:21:06,088
Les filles ?

397
00:21:09,128 --> 00:21:10,568
